  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Size of \"Next\" button in group chat screen is small. In result, it maybe hard to click it. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\"Next\" button have the same size as \"Create\":\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/36849610-c3dfcfe4-1d64-11e8-9c73-24d0b6a1043a.png\" width=\"300\">\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\"Next\" button size is really small. It's hard to tap:\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/36849691-f7808910-1d64-11e8-8fc6-5edb9269ddb8.png\" width=\"300\"> \r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Home\r\n- Create group chat\r\n- Select members for group chat\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly, March 1\r\n* Operating System: iOS only\r\n* Tested on iPhone 6, iOS 11.2.1",
